Introducing Home Screen! A place that we think you will spend a lot of time. Home Screen is a central place where you can watch more of the TV shows and movies that you love! We have created this area for you to more easily be able to find our newest and most popular content. We ve also added a touch of personalization by recommending a few shows and movies we hope that you will personally enjoy. And don t worry our Guide is still where you left it.

Get ready to be thrilled because our latest release is packed with exciting new features! New! We ve added a brand new area called My Stuff where you can organize more of the shows movies that you love! This replaces the My Recording area but don t worry because all of your recordings can now be found here and we have helped organize them! My Stuff combines Continue Watching with Recorded and Favorited content into one convenient location so it s super easy to find the stuff you care most about. New! We ve added the option for you to Favorite your desired movies and television shows access all the content you love in one place! New! Our newly designed TV Show View makes it easier than ever to explore watch and record from our extensive library of TV shows. Pick up right where you left off and get back to watching all the shows you enjoy.
